<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Account Activation</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h2>Welcome <%= name %>!</h2>
    <p>Thank you for registering with Cleverly. To activate your account, please use the following OTP code:</p>
    <h3 style="font-size: 24px; text-align: center; padding: 10px; background-color: #f5f5f5;"><%= otp %></h3>
    <p>This code will expire in 10 minutes.</p>
    <p>If you didn't request this registration, please ignore this email.</p>
    <br>
    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p>The Cleverly Team</p>
</body>
</html>